{"tid":544834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟聲明：因政治立場DQ違國際公約或削港自由開放聲譽","createTime":"2018-01-30T02:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T11:58:39.000Z","uid":23707,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"fba029c1c2748cd01492f5c5a1aed5aabc3b8a36","tid":544834,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:44:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180130/57770647\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180130%2F57770647&d=K0iBZ6rl8Rud6QRIZBRUztibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=773ffde1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180130%2F57770647&h=371db671\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180130/57770647</a>"},{"pid":"6c30061b3a7e383773aec5858515055632f110c3","tid":544834,"uid":23707,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:45:06.000Z","msg":"政府日前以香港眾志綱領倡議民主自決為藉口，進行政治審查，取消眾志常委周庭參加立法會港島區補選的資格。歐盟發言人發表聲明，指因候選人的政治立場而禁止其參選的做法，與《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》的權利相抵觸，亦有可能削弱香港作為自由開放社會的國際聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟聲明指出，選舉主任決定獲特區政府支持，而保障香港的公民權利和政治權利，是落實歐盟支持的「一國兩制」原則的重要組成部分，強調《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》透過《香港人權法案》在香港適用，公約保障選舉不受無理限制。<br />\n30名法律界選委昨亦發表聯合聲明，批評政府因周庭的政治聯繫及意見而剝削其參選權是不合理、不合法及違憲。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟聲明全文：<br />\nStatement by the Spokesperson on the decision to bar Agnes Chow from running for a Legislative Council by-election<br />\nThe decision by a Hong Kong returning officer to bar Agnes Chow from running for a Legislative Council by-election on the basis of her political affiliation, subsequently supported by the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region Government, risks diminishing Hong Kong's international reputation as a free and open society.<br />\nThe protection of civil and political rights in Hong Kong is an essential part of the implementation of the &quot;One Country, Two Systems&quot; principle, which the EU supports. Barring candidates from standing for election because of their political beliefs is in contradiction with the right under the International Covenant on Civil and Political Rights, whose application is guaranteed in Hong Kong by the Hong Kong Bill of Rights, to stand for election without unreasonable restrictions."},{"pid":"1a2aa3b9600985e3fabfdf9073b5e078275e9e53","tid":544834,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f577946123c9d2402c435da80d31fabc68af5a86","tid":544834,"uid":136994,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:47:32.000Z","msg":"全力支持歐盟即時取消香港旅遊同外交免簽待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇吓班權貴驚啲定平民驚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d80c0b0b5bb3fb911ee91611b674034c37cfe9e","tid":544834,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:47:40.000Z","msg":"大歐祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4506bb6855fa89d676d65e311455dd57a901c9","tid":544834,"uid":89530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:47:42.000Z","msg":"港共又鬧人干預架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d096366666f4836ea0b4204138bc5e290606c6e","tid":544834,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e4506bb6855fa89d676d65e311455dd57a901c9","tid":544834,"uid":89530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:47:42.000Z","msg":"港共又鬧人干預架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:49:38.000Z","msg":"講啲野好似清朝咁<br />\n快啲鎖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8b0a8bbe70d0ad7d8c3de3774f0f8afbb41c3b","tid":544834,"uid":5843,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy